# Modal / Dialog / Panel

**Figma:** [Modal / Dialog](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=128-10421&p=f&m=dev)

Structure, sizes, variants, and token mappings below are derived from Figma node 128:10421.

---

## Variables (from design-system-tokens.mdc)

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Surface | `--bg-base-default` |
| Backdrop | `--bg-blanket` |
| Header/body/footer border | `--border-base-default` |
| Secondary button | `--bg-base-tertiary` |
| Primary button | `--bg-brand-default` |
| Primary button text | `--text-brand-on-brand` |
| Close icon | `--text-base-default` |
| Dismiss text | `--text-base-secondary` |
| Selected nav item | `--bg-brand-tertiary` |

---

## Structure

- **Backdrop:** `--bg-blanket` (rgba(0,0,0,0.70)); optional backdrop-blur.
- **Surface:** `--bg-base-default`; rounded corners (Radius/200 or Radius/300).
- **Spacing:** Space tokens for header, body, footer gaps.

